{"id":23247,"name":"Mashable [Mobile] - Fixed width","category":"site","raw_subcategory":"mashable","subcategory":"mashable","style_tags":[],"description":"To those of you who think Mashable (mashable.com) is too messy, you should try out Mashable for mobile (m.mashable.com). Problem is, it's too damn wide! Here's a userstyle to make it at 800px width. Also changes the story borders to not be double.\r\nTested only in Google Chrome.","user":{"id":20794,"name":"henasraf","email":"redacted","paypal_email":"dokueki@gmail.com","homepage":null,"about":null,"license":null},"admin_delete_reason_id":null,"updated":"2009-12-11T07:26:40.000Z","weekly_install_count":0,"total_install_count":146,"rating":null,"screenshot_url":"https://userstyles.org/auto_style_screenshots/23247-after.png?r=1588493039","url":"/styles/23247/mashable-mobile-fixed-width","discussionsCount":0,"commentsCount":0,"css":"@-moz-document domain(m.mashable.com) {\r\n    body {text-align:center !important;}\r\n    body * {text-align:left !important;}\r\n    div.header,div.gui_link_wrap,p.link,.rss_link_bg {width:800px !important;margin:auto !important;}\r\n    .gui_link_wrap {border-top:none !important;}\r\n    .link + .gui_link_wrap {border-top:1px solid black !important;}\r\n}"}